            <title>[LU-10794] lfs quota did not work well for grace time output</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10794</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Following commit:&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10011&quot; title=&quot;suppress annoying messages for lfs quota&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10011&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10011&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; utils: refactor lfs quota codes&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Introduced a regression which will make &apos;lfs quota -t&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
will output nothing. this should be detected early in the regression&lt;br/&gt;
test, unluckily, there is no test in sanity-quota.sh to detect broken&lt;br/&gt;
function.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
